Name: Melanie Jones.

Description: Melanie Jones is a dedicated Music Production student with a strong passion for innovation and learning. Throughout their academic journey, they have gained experience in music production research and practical applications. They aspire to become a graphic designer creating innovative visual storytelling. Their dedication to excellence and problem-solving skills make them a promising professional in their field..
